        "content": "## ⏱ Clock In / Out\n\nDriver attendance. Two one-shot routes. Calls Fleet API `POST /attendance/clock-in|clock-out` (idempotent, reporting-window enforced server-side), maps the JSON result to a Hebrew message, sends it.\n\n**Routes:** `cmd_clock_in`, `cmd_clock_out`",
